title: Xueton Cai’s 2nd Place Run – 2016 Burton US Open Halfpipe
description: Smooth, technical and big enough airs to grab second place, Xuetong Cai was as close as anyone could come to taking Chloe Kim off the top spot.

transcripts: Donna Carpenters looking up at the pipe and the sun just popped, this just became a US open half pipe final it is beautiful outside and Xueton Cai started off with a big air to fakie. Shout out to Xueton for that one, absolutely into a cab 720, into the front side 900 so very technical combo from Xueton Cai into the backside 540, huge front side 7, so a huge variety of big variety of spins and then there's that switch air to fakie aka.
